'''Iziz Starport''', also known as the '''Royal Space Dock''',<ref name="TotJC">''[[Tales of the Jedi Companion]]''</ref> was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] that was located within [[Iziz/Legends|Iziz]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Onderon/Legends|Onderon]]. It was the largest spaceport in the system. A [[Beast Riders|Beast Rider]] kept caged [[cannok]]s and [[boma]]s in cages in a courtyard outside the hangars.

